==English==
===Adjectival Phrase===
'''[[philatelically]] [[inspired]]'''
# (stamp-collecting) an item produced by the [[postal]] authorities, but intended for [[stamp]] collectors rather than normal [[postage]] usage.
# a normal postal item, altered or [[enhanced]] in some way, to increase its appeal to collectors.  Eg, [[first day cover]]s, [[first flight cover]]s, etc.